<P>Smith, A. H., V. S. Evenson & D. H. Mitchel (1983). <I>The veiled species of</I> Hebeloma <I>in the western United States</I>. Ann Arbor: University of Michigan Press. 219 pp.</P>

<P>Smith, A. H. (1984). Studies of species of <I>Hebeloma</I> (Fr.) Kummer from the Great Lakes region of North America I. <I>Sydowia</I> 37: 271&ndash;283.</P>

